        <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">crosses</ENAMEX>, we amplified a region of 
        Tnfrh1 containing several of these
        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">SNPs</ENAMEX>. The PCR strategies generated products that crossed
