        these crosses, and showed a maternal expression bias, but
        weaker than that observed in fetal liver (data not shown).
        The parent-of-origin dependent allelic bias in 
        Tnfrh1 <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">mRNA</ENAMEX> was superimposed on a
        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">'baseline</ENAMEX>' bias towards hyper-expression of the <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">BL/6</ENAMEX> allele
